\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\",\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n  \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"linkedin_url_verified\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\": false,\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n  \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"recruiter_search_url\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\": \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"https://www.linkedin.com/search/results/people/?keywords=Company%20Name%20recruiter\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\",\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n  \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"careers_url\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\": \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\",\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n  \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"recruiters\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\": []\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n}\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n```\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\nAfter the batch, run the status command again and print this exact marker on its own line:\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n`=== SECTOR_BATCH_COMPLETE other <companies-touched> <entries-added> <remaining-unpopulated> <remaining-missing-descriptions> ===`\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\",\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"exit_code\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\":0,\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"status\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\":\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"completed\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"}}\\\\\\\\n./job/swarm/codex-sector-logs/other.jsonl:25:{\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"type\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\":\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"item.completed\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\",\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"item\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\":{\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"id\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\":\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"item_12\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\",\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"type\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\":\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"command_execution\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\",\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"command\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\":\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"/bin/zsh -lc 'rg \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"SECTOR_BATCH_COMPLETE\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\" job/swarm/sectors -n'\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\",\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"aggregated_output\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\":\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"job/swarm/sectors/logistics.md:128:`=== SECTOR_BATCH_COMPLETE logistics <companies-touched> <entries-added> <remaining-unpopulated> <remaining-missing-descriptions> ===`\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\njob/swarm/sectors/insurance.md:128:`=== SECTOR_BATCH_COMPLETE insurance <c