pe\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\":\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"agent_message\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\",\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"text\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\":\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"=== SECTOR_BATCH_COMPLETE defense 14 10 0 52 ===\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"}}\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\njob/swarm/codex-sector-logs/health-batch-0002-prompt.txt:26:=== SECTOR_BATCH_COMPLETE health <companies-touched> <entries-added> <remaining-unpopulated> <remaining-missing-descriptions> ===\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\njob/swarm/codex-sector-logs/cloud-batch-0006-prompt.txt:26:=== SECTOR_BATCH_COMPLETE cloud <companies-touched> <entries-added> <remaining-unpopulated> <remaining-missing-descriptions> ===\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\njob/swarm/codex-sector-logs/retail-batch-0004-prompt.txt:26:=== SECTOR_BATCH_COMPLETE retail <companies-touched> <entries-added> <remaining-unpopulated> <remaining-missing-descriptions> ===\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\njob/swarm/codex-sector-logs/logistics-batch-0002-prompt.txt:26:=== SECTOR_BATCH_COMPLETE logistics <companies-touched> <entries-added> <remaining-unpopulated> <remaining-missing-descriptions> ===\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\njob/swarm/codex-sector-logs/hardware-batch-0003-prompt.txt:26:=== SECTOR_BATCH_COMPLETE hardware <companies-touched> <entries-added> <remaining-unpopulated> <remaining-missing-descriptions> ===\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\njob/swarm/codex-sector-logs/bigtech-batch-0001-prompt.txt:26:=== SECTOR_BATCH_COMPLETE bigtech <companies-touched> <entries-added> <remaining-unpopulated> <remaining-missing-descriptions> ===\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\njob/swarm/codex-sector-logs/cloud-batch-0005-prompt.txt:26:=== SECTOR_BATCH_COMPLETE cloud <companies-touched> <entries-added> <remaining-unpopulated> <remaining-missing-descriptions> ===\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\njob/swarm/sectors/logistics.md:128:`=== SECTOR_BATCH_COMPLETE logistics <companies-touched> <entries-added> <remaining-unpopulated> <remaining-missing-descriptions> ===`\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\njob/swarm/codex-sector-logs/media-batch-0004-prompt.txt:26:=== SECTOR_BATCH_COMPLETE media <companies-touched> <entries-added> <remaining-unpopulated> <remaining-missing-descriptions> ===\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\njob/swarm/codex-sector-logs/defense-batch-0004-prompt.txt:26:=== SECTOR_BATCH_COMPLETE defense <companies-touched> <entries-added> <remaining-unpopulated> <remaining-missing-descriptions> ===\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\njob/swarm/codex-sector-logs/hardware.jsonl:46:{\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"type\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\":\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"item.completed\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\",\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"item\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\":{\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"id\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\":\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"item_1\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\",\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"type\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\":\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"command_execution\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\",\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"command\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\":\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"/bin/zsh -lc \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"sed -n '1,240p' job/swarm/sectors/hardware.md\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\",\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"aggregated_output\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\":\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"# Codex Sector Worker — Semiconductors / Hardware\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n**Assignment**\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n- Sector key: `hardware`\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n- Working file: `job/sectors/recruiter-hardware.json`\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n- Companies owned by this sector: 90\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n- You may edit **only** `job/sectors/recruiter-hardware.json`.\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n- Do not edit `job/recruiter.json`, UI copies, other sector files, or shared docs.\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n- Do not run the merge script. The orchestrator runs merges centrally after each batch to avoid write races.\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n**Mission**\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\nPopulate this sector with useful outreach data without repeating completed work:\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n1. Add or improve `company.description` for every company you touch, including companies that already have recruiters.\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n2. Populate empty `recruiters[]` arrays where credible public LinkedIn/web evidence exists.\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n3. Keep existing recruiter entries unless you can clearly tell they are stale or wrong.\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n4. After coverage is complete, deepen companies to a maximum of 10 contacts each.\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n5. After existing companies are deepened, add more companies in this sector, prioritizing Miami / South Florida and San Jose / Silicon Valley.\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n## Company Description Standard\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\nEvery touched company should have a concise description:\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n- 18-35 words, one sentence.\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n- Say what the company actually does and where it fits in the sector.\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n- Prefer concrete products, customers, or technical domain over marketing language.\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n- Mention SWE/AI relevance only when it is natural.\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n- Do not invent facts. If public data is thin, use a conservative description based on the company category and careers/company page.\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\nExample:\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n`\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"NVIDIA designs GPUs, AI accelerators, networking hardware, and software platforms used across data centers, gaming, autonomous systems, and applied machine learning.\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"`\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n## Recruiter Standard\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\nMinimum viable per company:\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n- Strong signals: add 2-3 current, relevant recruiters or talent partners, then move on.\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n- Weak signals: 1 recruiter is acceptable; for startups or thin teams, use a founder, CTO, VP Engineering, Head of Engineering, hiring manager, or technical lead.\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n- Prefer university, campus, emerging talent, early-career, intern, new grad, SWE, AI, ML, or technical recruiting titles.\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n- In bolster mode, technical members who are publicly hiring for their team are valid, especially for internship, new-grad, SWE, AI, ML, data, infrastructure, or product engineering roles.\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n- US-based or clearly US-hiring people are preferred.\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n- Never add more than 10 contacts to a company. If it already has 10 or more, skip it unless correcting stale data.\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n- Use only public professional information. Do not scrape aggressively.\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\nRecruiter object schema:\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n```json\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n{\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n  \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"name\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\": \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\",\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n  \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"title\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\": \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\